snippet.title: [Rhythm Bang] Game Trailer 2022
snippet.description:
Rhythm Bang is a rhythm based aiming game you can play with your mouse, and aim towards falling cubes that fall rhythmically to the hard electronic music that play throughout the levels! 

Steam store page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2156810/Rhythm_Bang/

Trailer by https://www.youtube.com/c/DigitalAzure
Music by https://www.youtube.com/c/St4bilityMusic
Rhythm Bang server: https://discord.gg/XrUssQEpJb
